\zoli1 \bd Golgotha nami nimesulibiwa pamoja na \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Mwokozi\bd*\bd ; na njia kwa Mungu Baba ni wazi, pazia limepasuka. \bd*
